title: Wordzable v1.1.9 for Windows
description:
OS: Windows 7, Windows 8, Windows Vista


By: LastEnd Entertainment


Language: English



Mix and twist jumbled letters to make words. Look for patterns and put your vocabulary to the test in over 47 stages containing over 450 levels that change each time you play. If you can find all the words in a stage, the next stage will unlock and allow you to return at any time. 

The free demo version contains 5 stages with 50 levels.
